{"tid":2517743,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB涉違規播政治廣告","createTime":"2021-05-05T13:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T17:59:33.000Z","uid":322378,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01d69ff1682e990fa064631c78777aceb7471197","tid":2517743,"uid":322378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"最近建制網媒堅料網係CCTVB賣廣告Sell國安法<br />\n但根據通訊局廣播條例<br />\n任何以大氣電波傳送免費電視訊號的電視台或電台<br />\n不得播放任何政治組織廣告<br />\n如2010年民建聯係商台落廣告+買時段做節目被通訊局罰款<br />\n而家CCTVB明目張膽播堅料網廣告<br />\n已經係赤裸裸政治宣傳！<br />\n大家要集體向通訊局投訴"},{"pid":"13855911c48f760de095c1bf16e91369d59eae24","tid":2517743,"uid":301050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">通訊局廣播條例</span><br />\n基本法都唔洗跟<br />\n呢條咩嚟"},{"pid":"3e2652cef287fb99b70fb28d156dcf10ec54264b","tid":2517743,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"502d242229b4d24f968742af057c098b74ea1849","tid":2517743,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:55:12.000Z","msg":"國安法&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;廣播條例"},{"pid":"10b769ee7f5560fb16006aba3d132c5af22ad0e8","tid":2517743,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"國安法凌駕一切，講咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}